    Real 'world.x_label.lines[1,1,1]'(unit = "m", quantity = "Length") "List of start and end points of cylinders resolved in an x-y frame defined by n_x, n_y, e.g., {[0,0;1,1], [0,1;1,0], [2,0; 3,1]}";
